      <title>悉尼主教刺伤事件后，澳大利亚反恐部队逮捕了七名青少年</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-counter-terrorism-force-arrests-seven-teenagers-after-sydney-bishop-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚反恐小组周三逮捕了七名与一名男孩有关的青少年，该男孩被控出于宗教动机对悉尼主教进行恐怖袭击，并对另外五人进行了讯问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-counter-terrorism-force-arrests-seven-teenagers-after-sydney-bishop-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾芯片制造商联华电子警告汽车和工业需求疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chipmaker-umc-warns-muted-auto-industrial-demand-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾芯片制造商联电周三表示，由于计算、消费和通信领域的库存水平改善，预计第二季度晶圆出货量将增加，但警告汽车和工业需求疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chipmaker-umc-warns-muted-auto-industrial-demand-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与共和党争斗后，拜登签署乌克兰援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/after-battle-with-republicans-biden-sign-ukraine-aid-package-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登将于周三签署一项法案，为乌克兰与俄罗斯的战争提供数十亿美元的新援助，这是总统在寻求连任之际取得的两党胜利，并为那些指望华盛顿提供帮助的盟友们带来鼓舞。支持基辅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/after-battle-with-republicans-biden-sign-ukraine-aid-package-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗、巴基斯坦呼吁联合国安理会对以色列采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/iran-pakistan-call-un-security-council-take-action-against-israel-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和巴基斯坦呼吁联合国安理会对以色列采取行动，称其“非法”袭击邻国和外国外交设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/iran-pakistan-call-un-security-council-take-action-against-israel-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:53:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行称中国支付宝+尚未申请许可</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indonesia-cenbank-says-chinas-alipay-yet-request-permit-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行副行长 Filianingsih Hendarta 在周三的新闻发布会上表示，中国蚂蚁集团旗下支付宝+尚未正式申请在印尼开展业务的许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indonesia-cenbank-says-chinas-alipay-yet-request-permit-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:29:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SK海力士将投资38.6亿美元在韩国生产DRAM芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/sk-hynix-invest-386-bln-dram-chip-production-base-south-korea-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国存储芯片制造商 SK 海力士周三表示，计划投资 5.3 万亿韩元（合 38.6 亿美元）在韩国建设新的动态随机存取存储器（DRAM）芯片生产基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/sk-hynix-invest-386-bln-dram-chip-production-base-south-korea-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:23:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行意外加息以稳定卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-central-bank-delivers-surprise-rate-rise-support-rupiah-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行周三出人意料地加息，加大力度支持卢比货币，由于避险情绪上升以及美国宽松政策的预期时间推迟，卢比货币已跌至四年来的低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-central-bank-delivers-surprise-rate-rise-support-rupiah-2024-04-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 07:52:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
