      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-central-bank-delivers-surprise-rate-hike-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行周三出人意料地加息，加大力度支持卢比货币，由于避险情绪上升以及美国宽松政策的预期时间推迟，卢比货币已跌至四年来的低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-central-bank-delivers-surprise-rate-hike-2024-04-24/</guid>
